Academic Spin-off of the Marche Polytechnic University
Aerodynamics, CFD analysis and drones experts.

Main Activities:
- Implementation and engineering of professional drones;
- Visible, thermographic and multispectral analysis with drones (underground oil pipeline monitoring, verification of the aging status of photovoltaic and wind power plants, etc ...);
- Thermofluidynamic CFD analysis;
- Software development for analysis and postprocessing of data.

